{"tid":295041,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"轉載-[民國舊史]-《 #中華民國廣告圖鑑 》","createTime":"2017-06-23T12:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T04:24:06.000Z","uid":122000,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"623d5c1da3fda334c74dad4d8d074350be67d133","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:29:01.000Z","msg":"轉自:秋海棠民國史地(驚敏感比人屌)<br />\n自上次[民國復興]偷[秋海棠民國史地]post事件後，見到論壇嘅重要性。故群主希望本人可以係連登開post。一來可以奪回內容主導權，二來可以推廣下民國鮮有提及嘅史料。一切歷史均會send番比群主親自回應<br />\n<br />\n回到正題<br />\n請多多支持<br />\ngroup link:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%A7%8B%E6%B5%B7%E6%A3%A0%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B2%E5%9C%B0-Glimpses-of-Modern-China-158517831018557/?fref=ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%25A7%258B%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25A3%25A0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%259C%25B0-Glimpses-of-Modern-China-158517831018557%2F%3Ffref%3Dts&d=1QGI8p%2BiiXw2c3H%2Bd%2BjoY%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fc928775\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%A7%8B%E6%B5%B7%E6%A3%A0%E6%B0%91%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B2%E5%9C%B0-Glimpses-of-Modern-China-158517831018557/?fref=ts</a><br />\n民國時期內憂外患，歷史背景複雜，政權更迭頻繁，戰亂不斷。我國民族資本企業在艱難的夾縫中求生存，同時大量的世界性托拉斯（Trust）壟斷組織湧入中國，也帶來許多新興之廣告形式。此時我民族企業與廣告畫家合作，創作大量優秀廣告畫，有香煙廣告、化妝品廣告、藥品廣告、銀行廣告、保險公司廣告等。尤其在對女性形象的描繪方面，從傳統美人到時尚女郎，把潮流時尚引領到一個全新階段，更代表當時社會審美之追求，成為社會理想形象。"},{"pid":"30c9b3e0d1dcd7d1c9267c933ee9fceb4512720f","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"1. <br />\n#華成煙公司出品 #美麗<br />\n《 漫畫界 - 民國廿五年（1936）第八期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17626384_671994629670872_1430605009033987665_n.jpg?oh=ec5c50958f2b583916c7d834fe0307b9&amp;oe=59E5F0EA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17626384_671994629670872_1430605009033987665_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dec5c50958f2b583916c7d834fe0307b9%26oe%3D59E5F0EA&h=a881e641&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5d4139357768280b0c66602f92af2c2a857ecad","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T18:56:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ad54513217b8729c2088cefb455570f29c283c3f","tid":295041,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T19:05:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"535bd043d1ba981475c0cd835521c90f5934d079","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T19:19:47.000Z","msg":"#世界第一兒科聖藥 #鷓鴣菜<br />\n《 經濟週刊 - 民國卅八年（1949）六月十八日出版 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17626358_672131269657208_761346863701132960_n.jpg?oh=f886d71b426a92db0d002e7362c048b9&amp;oe=59E82015\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17626358_672131269657208_761346863701132960_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df886d71b426a92db0d002e7362c048b9%26oe%3D59E82015&h=1c487f43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b894fd658ca506bf349b6a0709445fbcd71c4fa9","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"《 #致富良機 - #國民政府航空公路建設獎券（1936）》<br />\n<br />\n（開獎片段：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/158517831018557/videos/607720242764978/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F158517831018557%2Fvideos%2F607720242764978%2F%EF%BC%89&d=1QGI8p%2BiiXw2c3H%2Bd%2BjoY%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4c95b94f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/158517831018557/videos/607720242764978/）</a><br />\n<br />\n*民國廿二年（1933），上海工人之月薪一般為20元，雙職工家庭年收入為400元以上。技術工人、小學教師、醫護人員等家庭的月收入超過50元；中級職員、工程師、中學教員、醫生、記者、作家、律師和一般演員的家庭，月收入一、二百元以上。<br />\n<br />\n黃金十年，因糧食豐收，全國物價大致平穩，部分農產品還有所下降。舉例來說，漢口市場上，廿三年（1934）與廿四年（1935），一斤豬肉分別只有0.29和0.198元，而一百斤大米也從十五年（1926）7.55元跌到廿二年（1933）4.66元。如此同時，地價也隨之回落。抗戰前，江蘇鎮海縣畝產四百斤之農田，售價從十七年（1928）140元跌至70元，畝產三百斤之農田則從100元跌至40元。<br />\n<br />\n《 漫畫界 - 民國廿五年（1936）第七期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17626573_672195502984118_252640768012086660_n.jpg?oh=f2f8be99958234e7d187106d018bafe1&amp;oe=59E0FC97\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17626573_672195502984118_252640768012086660_n.jpg%3Foh%3Df2f8be99958234e7d187106d018bafe1%26oe%3D59E0FC97&h=b7ff7442&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc1d79619532289d6cc310efb86a0927772ac4a","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:13:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f2df57f92f78353ab38d54d075cc52f4a519bb53","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"#賓士油渣車 (Mercedes-Benz Diesel Buses）<br />\n《 中華汽車雜誌 - 民國廿二年（1933）第二期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17634726_672431672960501_6406936137423230800_n.jpg?oh=77931b9b1d7a3af77a2fadeffa6f8518&amp;oe=59CB2B09\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17634726_672431672960501_6406936137423230800_n.jpg%3Foh%3D77931b9b1d7a3af77a2fadeffa6f8518%26oe%3D59CB2B09&h=9f02dbbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b96be1d1c557a6070add9622a6bc47bb87a3956","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"ddaa500c67a09e41b7e78164d5a8ca4d014c0712","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"#先施公司總經理 #三鎗牌電單車 #司特林電池<br />\n《 中華汽車雜誌 - 民國廿二年（1933）第二期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17759816_672466869623648_6782924131982340506_n.jpg?oh=d9cc5863da78b055529e1d65d75c86ab&amp;oe=59C40DEC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17759816_672466869623648_6782924131982340506_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dd9cc5863da78b055529e1d65d75c86ab%26oe%3D59C40DEC&h=5de4115f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6bda44d1bba6bf5da75ae370ea1084e8b5f1c04","tid":295041,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e68935c66fb4e6cc441a9e5ab374fbbb4dfb7bb","tid":295041,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51a2e494e529dcae00960aa0bd74ee09209fbc00","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9b30e46b17d8f0028b353cd5be540f8fd798f4f8","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"#香港東方汽車公司總代理 #寶石牌貨車<br />\n《 中華汽車雜誌 - 民國廿二年（1933）第二期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17626355_672740372929631_7638580571293820251_n.jpg?oh=ad8c85e5681d0f7c8f9d8dee13c8c60c&amp;oe=59CD0C1C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17626355_672740372929631_7638580571293820251_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dad8c85e5681d0f7c8f9d8dee13c8c60c%26oe%3D59CD0C1C&h=3c0c5bea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af65c0d82bc30181fe2bf705f7ebd39dc3b17bf2","tid":295041,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed807c666bf753493f857a5bb72462a03445d60e","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"#華脱撲羅夫雨衣 （A.D.K. Waterproof Rain Coat)<br />\n#永新公司雨衣製造廠出品<br />\n《 中國漫畫 - 民國卅一年（1942）第一期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17759810_673059162897752_292047578237715138_n.jpg?oh=79fd9cd1eea4fcc584a0f94c8a7e1a2d&amp;oe=59CF6670\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17759810_673059162897752_292047578237715138_n.jpg%3Foh%3D79fd9cd1eea4fcc584a0f94c8a7e1a2d%26oe%3D59CF6670&h=0296f1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"376a5cca47a178677703b8b4c779a1aa054f786a","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:07:55.000Z","msg":"#天津義租界河沿一號 #福樂麗跳舞塲<br />\n<br />\n天津當年舞場聚集為英、法、德、俄租界以及南市等繁華地段，如聖安娜舞場、福祿林舞場等。為了招攬顧客，許多大飯店也以開設舞場為噱頭。作為當年的高檔娛樂場所，當時舞場中的舞客多為名媛、貴公子及洋人。隨著舞場的增加，以伴舞為業的舞女便應運而生。<br />\n<br />\n（資料來源：《 北洋畫報 - 民國廿一年（1932）第760期 》）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17796415_673608796176122_8750566618716224106_n.jpg?oh=95e2b918ece83f0d9ce62c3738043c7e&amp;oe=59C7F859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17796415_673608796176122_8750566618716224106_n.jpg%3Foh%3D95e2b918ece83f0d9ce62c3738043c7e%26oe%3D59C7F859&h=a46c321b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bef826b5f255f5e675a2fad59a7f3cfae411456e","tid":295041,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66dbeec544373577e71dfb866cfa79cf01877e74","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"#拜耳健身素 #德國拜耳藥廠 #笑容滿面<br />\n《 良友畫報 - 民國廿九年（1940）第一五六期 》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17799928_675539502649718_2254994426897453564_n.jpg?oh=2737a5f56bf9935565b9861e0a56cc3e&amp;oe=59D6362B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17799928_675539502649718_2254994426897453564_n.jpg%3Foh%3D2737a5f56bf9935565b9861e0a56cc3e%26oe%3D59D6362B&h=b0a2f57f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b1419566f1e68faf11a68891a1c6abc25a99a85","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"#德製祿萊福萊 #雙反相機 <br />\n#祿來福來反光鏡箱<br />\n<br />\n祿萊（Rollei）是一家製造光學產品的德國公司，以雙反相機祿萊福萊（Rolleiflex）著稱，該機成為人類攝影史上經典中的經典。*廣告商品為 Rolleiflex Standard 6x6 K2（亦稱 Rolleiflex Old Standard Model 6RF 620）<br />\n<br />\n《 飛鷹攝影雜誌 - 民國廿五年（1936）雙十節特大號（第十期）》<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17759885_678870852316583_6071242663262023189_n.jpg?oh=6217ee31b44d97a95d91e69e2e15c628&amp;oe=59C8E138\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17759885_678870852316583_6071242663262023189_n.jpg%3Foh%3D6217ee31b44d97a95d91e69e2e15c628%26oe%3D59C8E138&h=61de5c2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6b7044ea9a09bb834deece7158273b21932f0da","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"#史的勒電梯（STIGLER）<br />\n<br />\n創製於西曆一八七〇年，積六十餘年之製造經驗。業己裝置三萬五千餘具，年造電梯兩千四百具。<br />\n<br />\n《 中國建築 - 民國廿二年（1933）第一卷第三期 》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17884655_679447292258939_1651843204312581510_n.jpg?oh=cae39d7f06b18d47c069c928d00eeb60&amp;oe=59FFBF82\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17884655_679447292258939_1651843204312581510_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dcae39d7f06b18d47c069c928d00eeb60%26oe%3D59FFBF82&h=10c82163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a94f0a9d113253483cfddc1f7737178b546060","tid":295041,"uid":122000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T16:36:11.000Z","msg":"#新仁記營造廠<br />\n《 建築月刊 - 民國廿三年（1934）第二卷第四期 》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17861655_679530368917298_5393026829506126255_n.jpg?oh=d03f9754303dfab3c4c25bbb6b7e95df&amp;oe=5A0B9E08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17861655_679530368917298_5393026829506126255_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dd03f9754303dfab3c4c25bbb6b7e95df%26oe%3D5A0B9E08&h=86de38ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1775c0586ac0f5570df9882f41557d390302fe55","tid":295041,"uid":14541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"Lm 學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da54b3f4324cbb8888485d989e24db83382550b0","tid":295041,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T04:24:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}